	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_39664153"><p>So we are splitting hairs about the definition of a cogent argument? OK... I will accept that my choice of phrase must have been wrong (I certainly wasn't quoting anyone else directly), and happily substitute your, more accurate and precise wording.</p></div>
	</div>

