		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~superwiz">superwiz <span class="uid">(655733)</span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_39662101">		
		on Thursday April 12, @02:33PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2782855&amp;cid=39662101">#39662101</a>)
